OL,3,CRetail spending heats up in June due
OL,4,Cto warm weather ` BRC
OL,6,FUK retailers saw sales lift higher in
OL,7,FJune as warmer weather helped drive
OL,8,Fmore shoppers onto the high street,
OL,9,Faccording to new figures.
OL,11,FFresh data from the British Retail
OL,12,FConsortium (BRC) showed shopping
OL,13,Factivity swung higher for the month as
OL,14,Fsales of fans and sportswear rose
OL,15,Fsharply due to the recent hot spell
OL,16,Fand sporting events such as Wimbledon.
