OL,3,CRetail spending heats up in June due
OL,4,Cto warm weather ` BRC
OL,6,FThe monthly BRC-KPMG retail sales
OL,7,Fmonitor revealed that total UK retail
OL,8,Fsales increased by 3.1% in June year-
OL,9,Fon-year, compared with a 0.2% in the
OL,10,Fsame month a year earlier.
OL,12,FThis was also particularly buoyed by
OL,13,Fan increase in food sales, which grew
OL,14,Fby 4.1% for the month on the back of
OL,15,Faccelerating price inflation.
OL,17,FRecent figures from the trade group
OL,18,Fshowed that food inflation increased
OL,19,Fto 3.7% in June, while fresh food was
OL,20,F3.2% more expensive than a year ago.
