OL,6,F"Food sales remained strong, though
OL,7,Fthis was in part driven by food
OL,8,Finflation, which has risen steadily
OL,9,Fover the course of the year."
OL,11,FLinda Ellett, UK head of consumer,
OL,12,Fretail and leisure at KPMG, said:
OL,13,F"Home appliances and homeware
OL,14,Fpurchases helped retail sales to grow
OL,15,Fin June, as new homebuyers and those
OL,16,Fhaving a refresh in their current home
OL,17,Ftook advantage of summer promotions
OL,18,Fboth in-store and online."
