OL,3,CRetail spending heats up in June due
OL,4,Cto warm weather ` BRC
OL,6,FNevertheless, similar spending data
OL,7,Ffrom Barclays painted a slightly
OL,8,Fdifferent picture, pointing towards a
OL,9,Fmarginal dip in monthly spending.
OL,11,FIt reported that consumer card
OL,12,Fspending was 0.1% lower in June, as
OL,13,Fessential spending dropped for the
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FBarclays said essential spending was
OL,17,Fdown 2.1% for the month, according to
OL,18,Fits card data, despite the improvement
OL,19,Fin weather.
